Moon.
Company: Tactics
Release date: Nov 21, 1997
Genre: Visual Novel


Summary: The story follows a young girl named Amasawa Ikumi who follows the recent death of her mother to an organization known as FARGO. Ikumi joins FARGO and uncovers their disturbing nature of harnessing psychic abilities through torture.



Team: Amaterasu Translations



